  "frame_eqs": "dec_m = pow (0.85, 30/fps); dec_s = pow (0.9, 30/fps);\n\nbeat = bass+mid+treb;\navg = avg*dec_s + beat*(1-dec_s);\nis_beat = above(beat, .4+avg+peak) * above (time, t0+.2);\nt0 = is_beat*time + (1-is_beat)*t0;\npeak = is_beat * beat + (1-is_beat)*peak*dec_m;\nindex = (index + is_beat) %32;\nindex2 = (index2 + is_beat*bnot(index))%8;\nindex3 = (index3 + is_beat* if(bnot(rand(8)%2),-1,1)*bnot(index%16))%6;\n\nq20 = avg;\nq22 = peak;\nq24 = is_beat;\nq27 = index +1;\nq28 = index2;\nZDist =  .3 + .4*pow(sin(.5*(xang+zang_-movy)),4); //zoom ;\nq29 = .12/ZDist ;\n\nq30 = int(time*8) * .0 *  (index2%2); //lower zones shift\nq31 = above (beat,avg*2) * (beat-avg*2);\n\ndir = dir*dec_s + (1-dec_s)*index3*3.1416*1/2;\nspeed = .08 + .14*(index2%2)*ZDist;\nmovx = movx + cos(dir)*pow(cos(dir),8)/fps*speed ;\nmovy = movy + sin(dir)*pow(sin(dir),8)/fps*speed ;\nmonitor = index3;\n\nxang =  -cos((zang_+movx+movy*2)+time*.1) * .7;;\nq5 = movx; q6 = movy;;\nyang = 0;\ntmp = sin(8* (movx+movy))  ;\nzang_ = zang_ + tmp*pow(tmp,6)/fps/(pow(xang,2)+.05)/2*sin(time/2.5);\npulse = q27 * bnot((2+index2)%4);\nzang = zang_+pulse ;\n\nox = -0; oy = .0; oz = ZDist;\nmx = ox*cos(zang) - oy*sin(zang);\nmy = ox*sin(zang) + oy*cos(zang);\nox = mx;oy = my;\nmx = ox*cos(yang) + oz*sin(yang);\nmz = - ox*sin(yang) + oz*cos(yang);\nox = mx;oz = mz;\nmy = oy*cos(xang) - oz*sin(xang);\nmz = oy*sin(xang) + oz*cos(xang);\noy = my;oz = mz;\nq11=ox; q12 = oy; q13 = oz; //Position\n\n//Vektor x nach rechts\nox = 1; oy = 0; oz = 0;\nmx = ox*cos(zang) - oy*sin(zang);\nmy = ox*sin(zang) + oy*cos(zang);\nox = mx;oy = my;\nmx = ox*cos(yang) + oz*sin(yang);\nmz = - ox*sin(yang) + oz*cos(yang);\nox = mx;oz = mz;\nmy = oy*cos(xang) - oz*sin(xang);\nmz = oy*sin(xang) + oz*cos(xang);\noy = my;oz = mz;\nq14=ox; q15 = oy; q16 = oz;\n\n\n//Vektor z nach hinten\nox = 0; oy = 0; oz = 1;;\n\nmx = ox*cos(zang) - oy*sin(zang);\nmy = ox*sin(zang) + oy*cos(zang);\nox = mx;oy = my;\nmx = ox*cos(yang) + oz*sin(yang);\nmz = - ox*sin(yang) + oz*cos(yang);\nox = mx;oz = mz;\nmy = oy*cos(xang) - oz*sin(xang);\nmz = oy*sin(xang) + oz*cos(xang);\noy = my;\noz = mz;\nq17=ox; q18 = oy; q19 = oz;",
